ith patios, pet stores, and dog-friendly beaches.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d guide-section\"><h4 class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Key Features</h4><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d features-chips\"><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d feature-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-check-circle-fill\"></i>Outdoor seating</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d feature-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-check-circle-fill\"></i>Water bowls</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d feature-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-check-circle-fill\"></i>Dog treats</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d feature-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-check-circle-fill\"></i>Pet products</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d feature-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-check-circle-fill\"></i>Social atmosphere</span></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d guide-section\"><h4 class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Best For</h4><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d best-for-list\"><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d best-for-tag\">Casual outings</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d best-for-tag\">Dining with pets</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d best-for-tag\">Shopping trips</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d best-for-tag\">Social experiences</span></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d guide-section\"><h4 class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">What to Bring</h4><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-list\"><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Leash</span></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Portable water bowl</span></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Calm temperament</span></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Training treats</span></div></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d guide-section\"><h4 class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Pro Tips</h4><ul class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d tips-list\"><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Call ahead to confirm pet policy</li><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Keep your dog leashed at all times</li><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Ensure your dog is well-behaved in public</li><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Respect other customers</li><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Be prepared to leave if your dog becomes anxious</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d card-footer\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d expand-toggle\"><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">View guide</span><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-chevron-down\"></i></button><a class=\"jump-link\" href=\"#dog-friendly-establishment-parks\">Jump to list<i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-arrow-right\"></i></a></div></article></div></section></div></div></section><section id=\"map-and-neighborhoods\" class=\"map-experience-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Interactive planning</span><h2>See everything laid out on the map</h2><p>Use the live map to lock in nearby options, preview ratings, and save time hopping between neighborhoods.</p></div><div class=\"map-grid\"><div class=\"map-panel\"><!--$!--><template data-dgst=\"BAILOUT_TO_CLIENT_SIDE_RENDERING\"></template><div style=\"min-height:320px;background:#f3f4f6\"></div><!--/$--></div><div class=\"map-sidebar\"><div class=\"map-sidebar-card\"><h3>Quick filters</h3><div class=\"map-chip-grid\"><button type=\"button\"><span>Dog-Friendly Establishment</span><small>1</small></button></div></div><div class=\"map-sidebar-card\"><h3>Highest-rated nearby</h3><div class=\"mini-park-list\"><div class=\"mini-park-card\"><div><p>Animal Activity Center, Inc.</p><span>Dog-Friendly Establishment</span></div><strong>4.3</strong></div></div></div><div class=\"map-sidebar-card muted\"><p>Tip: tap any map marker to open directions, amenities, and current open hours.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"planning-essentials\" class=\"planning-essentials-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Visit toolkit</span><h2>Plan the perfect dog outing in <!-- -->Clinton Township</h2><p>Borrow best practices from local trainers, rangers, and experienced pet parents.</p></div><div class=\"planning-grid\"><article class=\"planning-card\"><div class=\"planning-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-clock-history\"></i></div><h3>Peak &amp; quiet windows</h3><ul><li>6–9 AM: high energy social hour</li><li>10 AM–3 PM weekdays: calm training-friendly window</li><li>After 4 PM: sunset crowd + cooler temps</li></ul></article><article class=\"planning-card\"><div class=\"planning-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-backpack\"></i></div><h3>Essentials checklist</h3><ul><li>Leash + harness for entry/exit control</li><li>Collapsible water bowl and fresh water</li><li>Plenty of waste bags and high-value treats</li></ul></article><article class=\"planning-card\"><div class=\"planning-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-shield-check\"></i></div><h3>Local regulations</h3><ul><li>Keep proof of vaccinations or city license handy</li><li>Voice control required in most off-leash zones</li><li>Limit three dogs per handler in public parks</li></ul></article><article class=\"planning-card\"><div class=\"planning-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-heart\"></i></div><h3>Community etiquette</h3><ul><li>Scan the park before entering and remove prong collars</li><li>Monitor play styles and intervene early</li><li>Share shaded space and refill water when you&#x27;re done</li></ul></article></div></div></section><section id=\"owner-cta\" class=\"owner-cta-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Partner with us</span><h2>Feature your Clinton Township dog park</h2><p>Upgrade to a featured listing, share live availability, or pitch a new indoor concept. Our team drives qualified local pet parents every week.</p><div class=\"hero-cta-row\" style=\"margin-top:24px\"><a class=\"hero-cta primary\" href=\"/list-your-park\">List a property</a><a class=\"hero-cta ghost\" href=\"/contact\">Contact the team</a></div></div></section><section id=\"park-directory\" class=\"park-directory-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">City directory</span><h2>All dog parks in <!-- -->Clinton Township</h2><p>Filter-ready cards with ratings, amenities, and quick actions. Use the chips to jump between sections.</p></div><div class=\"category-chip-row\"><button type=\"button\">Dog-Friendly Establishment</button></div><div id=\"dog-friendly-establishment-parks\" class=\"directory-category\"><div class=\"directory-header\"><div><h3>Dog-Friendly Establishment<!-- -->s<!-- --> in <!-- -->Clinton Township</h3><p>1<!-- --> locations ·<!-- --> <!-- -->4.3<!-- --> <!-- -->average rating</p></div><span class=\"directory-count\">1</span></div><div class=\"directory-grid\"><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/animal-activity-center-inc\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Animal Activity Center, Inc.</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">unknown</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>4</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Hours vary by season</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Clinton Township<!-- -->, <!-- -->MI</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"><span class=\"premium-badge feature-badge\">PARKING</span></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">Dog parents in Clinton Township choose Animal Activity Center, Inc. for their pet care needs. This facility features state-of-the-art indoor play areas, compassionate staff members, offering pet care. Their services supports your dog&#x27;s physical and mental well-being. situated in a prime Clinton Township location. Book your dog&#x27;s stay at Animal Activity Center, Inc. today</p></div></a></div></div><div class=\"thin-content-box\" style=\"margin-top:2rem;padding:2rem;background:#f8fafc;border-radius:12px;text-align:center\"><h3 style=\"font-size:1.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem\">Know a great dog park in <!-- -->Clinton Township<!-- -->?</h3><p style=\"color:#64748b;margin-bottom:1.5rem;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto 1.5rem\">We are actively scouting for more indoor and dog-friendly parks in <!-- -->Clinton Township<!-- -->. If you know a hidden gem, help the community by adding it to our directory.</p><a class=\"hero-cta primary\" style=\"display:inline-flex\" href=\"/list-your-park\">Submit a Park</a></div></div></section><section id=\"faq-section\" class=\"city-faq-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><section id=\"faq-section\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-section\"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-shell\"><div aria-labelledby=\"faq-heading\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-header\"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a section-eyebrow\">Helpful Information</span><h2 id=\"faq-heading\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Frequently asked questions about <!-- -->Clinton Township<!-- --> dog parks</h2><p class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Real-world guidance covering pricing, safety, etiquette, and planning for more than <!-- -->1<!-- --> parks and dog-friendly spaces across <!-- -->Clinton Township<!-- -->. Tap a topic to reveal deeper context.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-header-meta\"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a meta-card\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a meta-label\">Answer library</span><strong class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">4</stron